reviewText: the grades of the last quiz is not well configured
Good to know fundamentals of IOT and IIOT with AWS knowledge.
Good for introduction IIoT in AWS
Very good overview of AWS IIoT.The exercise instructions were made for a previous version of AWS and should be updated.
Good for introduction. AWS can give more examples of different industrial domains like Steel, Continuous Process industries etc
Excellent introduction to Industrial IoT with nice exercises. Concise and clear for industrial automation practitioners to get started with the emerging IIoT for their plants using AWS services.
Lots of cutting information from one of the world's premiere cloud service providers as to IIoT.  Instructor Neil in particular was brilliant and entertaining.
This courser is awesome. I learnet so many things, and I recommend freshers to learn this course.

Although I have used the services discussed in this course several times, the course gave me a narrative and flow of how the services come together to offer a robust, secure and reliable IIoT architecture. Certainly enjoyed it :) Looking forward to the next one that stitches the ML part to this.
